biography: Alejandro is the Director of the Markets AI, Data & Platform at Zalando SE, where he is responsible for petabyte-scale AI & Data platforms that power the Pricing, Traffic and Trading technology across the group. He is also Scientific Advisor at the Institute for Ethical AI, where he has led contributions to EU policy, including the AI Act, the Data Act and the Digital Services Act, among others. Alejandro is currently appointed as AI Expert at the United Nations and the European Commission, and serves as Board Member at the ACM's Board of Directors.
